                    <GeometryDrawing Geometry="F1 M 22,4L 1122,4C 1131.94,4 1140,12.0588 1140,21.9999L 1140,454C 1140,463.941 1131.94,472 1122,472L 22,472C 12.0588,472 4,463.941 4,454L 4,21.9999C 4,12.0588 12.0588,4 22,4 Z ">
